   Sort Method: quicksort  Memory: xxxkB
   ->  Subquery Scan on agg_stage_1 (actual rows=3 loops=1)
         Output: agg_stage_1.document, bson_orderby(agg_stage_1.document, '{ "_id" : { "$numberInt" : "1" } }'::bson)
         ->  GroupAggregate (actual rows=3 loops=1)
               Output: bson_repath_and_build('_id'::text, (bson_expression_get(collection.document, '{ "" : "$x" }'::bson, true, '{ "now" : NOW_SYS_VARIABLE }'::bson)), 'f'::text, bsonfirstonsorted(bson_expression_get(collection.document, '{ "" : "$y" }'::bson, true, '{ "now" : NOW_SYS_VARIABLE }'::bson))), (bson_expression_get(collection.document, '{ "" : "$x" }'::bson, true, '{ "now" : NOW_SYS_VARIABLE }'::bson))
               Group Key: bson_expression_get(collection.document, '{ "" : "$x" }'::bson, true, '{ "now" : NOW_SYS_VARIABLE }'::bson)
               ->  Index Scan using idx_x on documentdb_data.documents_21000 collection (actual rows=8 loops=1)
